# Reason Codes

## Why reason codes?

Reason codes are stable identifiers used for:
- application branching
- audit queries
- CI assertions (policy tests)

## Examples (illustrative)

- TOOL_NOT_ALLOWED
- PII_DETECTED
- COST_BUDGET_EXCEEDED
- PROMPT_INJECTION_DETECTED
